  "body": "## What's Changed\r\n* ci: Add workflow to publish built layers as artifacts by @CarlesDD in https://github.com/DataDog/datadog-lambda-js/pull/750\r\n* Fix negative duration on aws.apigateway.authorizer span by @pablomartinezbernardo in https://github.com/DataDog/datadog-lambda-js/pull/751\r\n* chore(deps): bump dd-trace to v5.93.0 by @pablomartinezbernardo in https://github.com/DataDog/datadog-lambda-js/pull/749\r\n* v12.137.0 by @pablomartinezbernardo in https://github.com/DataDog/datadog-lambda-js/pull/753\r\n\r\n>[!IMPORTANT]\r\n> This version imports `dd-trace-js` [v5.93.0](https://github.com/DataDog/dd-trace-js/releases/tag/v5.93.0)\r\n\r\n## New Contributors\r\n* @pablomartinezbernardo made their first contribution in https://github.com/DataDog/datadog-lambda-js/pull/751\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/DataDog/datadog-lambda-js/compare/v12.136.0...v12.137.0\r\n\r\n```yml\r\n# AWS Commercial\r\narn:aws:lambda:<AWS_REGION>:464622532012:layer:Datadog-Node18-x:137\r\narn:aws:lambda:<AWS_REGION>:464622532012:layer:Datadog-Node20-x:137\r\narn:aws:lambda:<AWS_REGION>:464622532012:layer:Datadog-Node22-x:137\r\narn:aws:lambda:<AWS_REGION>:464622532012:layer:Datadog-Node24-x:137\r\n\r\n# AWS GovCloud\r\narn:aws-us-gov:lambda:us-gov-<AWS_REGION>:<ACCOUNT>:layer:Datadog-Node18-x:137\r\narn:aws-us-gov:lambda:us-gov-<AWS_REGION>:<ACCOUNT>:layer:Datadog-Node20-x:137\r\narn:aws-us-gov:lambda:us-gov-<AWS_REGION>:<ACCOUNT>:layer:Datadog-Node22-x:137\r\narn:aws-us-gov:lambda:us-gov-<AWS_REGION>:<ACCOUNT>:layer:Datadog-Node24-x:137\r\n\r\nACCOUNT =\r\n002406178527 for us1 environment\r\n486696501492 for us2 environment\r\n```",
